# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# i3 config used as an example for configuring dwm
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Notation:
# +++++ - works in dwm
# ***** - is substituted by some other command, or irrelevant to dwm
# ----- - does not work in dwm yet
#
# A few things that also do not work so far:
#
# * Everything is moved to the first workspace on dwm recompile + reinstall
# * Programs do not open on their indicated workspaces
# * Focusing programs do not open their workspace
# * Jetbrains ???
# * Picom focuses windows incorrectly (reverse behaviour)
# * dmwblocks do not update at all
# * multi-screen functionality does not work (or I just haven't learnt how to use it)
# * Extra XF86 keys: Raise/Lower Volumne and Brightness Up/Down keys do not work
#       Other XF86 keys in dwm behave just the same as in i3
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  _ _____                    __ _
# (_)___ /    ___ ___  _ __  / _(_) __ _
# | | |_ \   / __/ _ \| '_ \| |_| |/ _` |
